Returns {{c|true}} if the iterator encountered the end-of-file condition, that is, if an earlier call to {{lc|std::basic_streambuf::sputc}} (made by {{rlpt|1=operator=}}) returned {{c|Traits::eof}}.

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
{{c|true}} if this iterator has encountered the end-of-file condition on output, {{c|false}} otherwise.
